data.description: Almost NEW...This Home was Built in 2020 and SHOWS Beautifully!!  This is a GREAT Mobile/Manufactured Home sitting on an EXTRA LARGE Lot!!  Per the owners, the City will be PAVING the road in the near future * SPACIOUS Floorplan offering 1500sqft with 3 LARGE Bedrooms and 2 FULL Bathrooms * * * ISLAND Kitchen with SOLID Counter Tops, Additional Cabinetry added, Breakfast Counter for the Kids, Recessed Lighting and In-Kitchen Dining Area * * Large Living Room with HIGH Pitched Ceilings, Beautiful Wood Laminate/Vinyl Flooring Throughout and Ceiling Fan * * INDOOR LAUNDRY ROOM * * Terrific Backyard with Covered Patio, Storage Shed, Fruit Trees, Large Side Yard with Plenty of Grass for the Kids to Play * * Spacious Master Bedroom with HIGH Ceilings - AND - Private MASTER Bath with His/Her Sinks and Tub/Shower Combo * * 2 Additional Nicely Appointed Bedrooms * * Large Front Covered Porch to Enjoy the Evening Breeze * * Close to Schools, Parks, Shopping, Dining...and LOW LOW TAXES & NO HOA or SOLAR FEES * * Submit ALL OFFERS -  Seller is Motivated!!
